<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Welcome to the WFL Affiliate Program </span></span></span></h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><img alt="WFL Affiliate Program" height="101" src="{SITEURL}userfiles/media/Dollar Sign Smiley Facea.jpg" title="WFL Affiliate Program" width="200" /><br /></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: small;">We have a new Shareasale affiliate account that has instant payouts.&nbsp; Please click <a href="http://www.shareasale.com/shareasale.cfm?merchantID=30147">here</a> to learn more.</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Why should you become a WFL affiliate?</span></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">1) High payouts that are three levels deep -- 25%, 15%, and 5%.<br /></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">2) No product price increase like traditional MLM programs. The Genesis Platinum is only $1695!<br /></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">3) Free extensive back office to control your customers, sales, and downline.</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">4) Free state-of-the-art affiliate website that you can customize to fit your business.</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">5) Free use of our impact video (you can view it on our home page) to drive customers to your site. &nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Between the free video and the free affiliate site, <strong>we do the sales pitch for you.</strong>&nbsp; All you have to do is find people to send to your video and site.&nbsp; <br /></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Here's how it works:</span><br /></span></span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">You earn a<span style="color: #ff0000;"> 25%</span> commission on all of your direct sales!&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Those who buy direct from you then can sign up as an affiliate under you (in your "downline") and you earn a <span style="color: #ff0000;">15%</span> commission on all of the direct sales that they make!&nbsp; <br /></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Then, you also earn a <span style="color: #ff0000;">5%</span> commission on all of the direct sales that your second level affiliates make!&nbsp; </span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">For example, here is a tier tree of one of our affiliates.&nbsp;Those affiliates directly beneath him are on his first level, so he earns 25% on each of their sales.&nbsp;Those beneath his first-level affiliates&nbsp;are on his second level, so he gets 15% on their sales. Then the affiliates beneathe <em>those</em> affiliates are on his third level, so he gets 5%. Take a look at all the affiliates he has gathered -- he makes money every time anyone makes a sale!<br /></span></span></p>
