<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">It only takes four sales to recoup the money you spent on your Genesis.&nbsp;25% of $1695 x 4 = <span style="color: #ff0000;">$1695<span style="color: #000000;">.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">If the four people you sold to sell four Water for Life USA Genesis units, you earn 15% of $1695 x 16, or <span style="color: #ff0000;">$4068.00!</span><br /></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">If each of those people sell four water ionizers, that's 64&nbsp;people on your third level times 5% which is an additional <span style="color: #ff0000;">$5424.00!</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">Is there an easier way to make <span style="color: #ff0000;">$9,492.00!?</span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">&nbsp;</span>What distinguishes our three-tier program from other affiliate marketing programs is that <em><strong>we don't raise the price of our product in order to accommodate too many tiers.</strong></em>&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">We at Water for Life USA believe in offering honest products at an honest price.&nbsp; Feel free to contact us anytime for help in navigating the murky sales waters that have been muddied by many involved in this industry.<br /></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">The Water for Life USA Affiliate program offers:</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">Best product + Affordable price + Big commission payouts = High volume and very high earnings for you!</span></span></span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">We also support our affiliates like no other water ionizer company.&nbsp;When you sign up as a WFL affiliate, we will set up for you your own five-page mini affiliate website! This five-page site comes complete with videos, testimonials, articles, and is customizable by you so that you can add your own content!&nbsp; The most amazing part of this five-page site is that it is independent of our site, which means you can process orders and sign up new affiliates directly from your own site!&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Plus it's free!&nbsp; No startup fees!&nbsp; No monthly maintenance fees!&nbsp; <br /></strong></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">Also, after you sign up, you will be given access to use the WFL impact video. This is a compact three minute presentation of ionized water and our products that you can email to all of your business contacts. Your WFL impact video links directly to your new affiliate mini-site. So, between the video and the site, the sales work is done for you!</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">To sign up as a WFL affiliate today, click on the register button on the top right side of this page.&nbsp; Fill out your name and contact information including the name of the referring affiliate and the order number of your water ionizer purchase.&nbsp;If you were not referred to WFL by someone, then just enter the order number.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">The WFL affiliate program is the best way to get the word out about water ionizers and make money! You are also backed up by Water for Life USA, one of the oldest and most respected water ionizer distributors in the US. <strong>Sign up today and create a better future for yourself and your family.</strong> <br /></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Please don't hesitate to contact us anytime with questions.&nbsp;<br /><br />Warm regards,&nbsp;<br /><br />Your Water for Life USA staff<br />www.waterforlifeusa.com<br />1-877-255-3713</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br /></span></span></p>